snippet.title: Rayman Legends: Definitive Edition on Nintendo Switch: Michel Ancel Interview
snippet.description:
Rayman, winner of multiple artistic and musical achievements, is coming to Nintendo Switch™ with Rayman® Legends Definitive Edition! 
 
 Hear from Michel Ancel about what to expect. 
 
 Learn more at: https://www.ubisoft.com/en-US/game/rayman-legends-definitive-edition/.
